            simple and unobtrusive as possible. I won't plague you with another rant on free
            software, there's a million of those out there so
            <a 
                class="text-nat-white-c01 no-underline hover:text-nat-black-c01 hover:bg-nat-white-c01"
                href="">
                [here]
            </a>
            and
            <a 
                class="text-nat-white-c01 no-underline hover:text-nat-black-c01 hover:bg-nat-white-c01"
                href="https://archive.ph/21b4o">
                [here]
            </a>
            is one. As that is not the main reason I use it, but just that it works for me.
        </div>

        <h1>Posts</h1>
